 서비스를 확대하겠다\"고 말했다.","url":"https://www.mt.co.kr/estate/2026/05/13/2026051315384418493","published_at":"2026-05-13T17:44:00","sentiment":"positive","is_new":true}],"disclosures":[{"date":"2026-05-13T17:09:30","title":"기업설명회(IR)개최(안내공시)              ","url":"https://dart.fss.or.kr/dsaf001/main.do?rcpNo=20260513801010","is_new":true},{"date":"2026-05-12T09:11:26","title":"임원ㆍ주요주주특정증권등소유상황보고서","url":"https://dart.fss.or.kr/dsaf001/main.do?rcpNo=20260512000014","is_new":false},{"date":"2026-05-08T16:57:29","title":"[기재정정]단일판매ㆍ공급계약체결              ","url":"https://dart.fss.or.kr/dsaf001/main.do?rcpNo=20260508800984","is_new":false}],"reports":[],"consensus":{"Q":{"period":"2026년 2분기","latest":200405263157.88998,"is_new":false,"series":[{"date":"2026-04-13","value":191182352941.18},{"date":"2026-04-14","value":190982352941.18},{"date":"2026-04-15","value":191394117647.06},{"date":"2026-04-16","value":191158823529.41},{"date":"2026-04-20","value":192394117647.06},{"date":"2026-04-21","value":191816666666.66998},{"date":"2026-04-24","value":191405263157.88998},{"date":"2026-04-29","value":199635000000.0},{"date":"2026-04-30","value":198585000000.0},{"date":"2026-05-06","value":197510526315.79},{"date":"2026-05-08","value":200405263157.88998}]},"Y":{"period":"2026년","latest":828455000000.0,"is_new":false,"series":[{"date":"2026-04-13","value":810795238095.24},{"date":"2026-04-14","value":809680952380.95},{"date":"2026-04-15","value":810828571428.5701},{"date":"2026-04-16","value":809590476190.48},{"date":"2026-04-20","value":807066666666.6699},{"date":"2026-04-21","value":810735000000.0},{"date":"2026-04-24","value":812285714285.71},{"date":"2026-04-29","value":826757142857.1399},{"date":"2026-04-30","value":826423809523.81},{"date":"2026-05-06","value":826805000000.0},{"date":"2026-05-08","value":828455000000.0}]}},"briefing":{"briefing":"이번 상승은 압구정 3·5구역에 고급 시니어 서비스를 도입하는 발표와 관련이 있습니다. 이러한 혁신적인 서비스 모델은 현대건설의 차별화된 주거 상품을 통해 시장에서 긍정적인 반응을 이끌어낼 것으로 기대됩니다.","content_url":"https